<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title> 작성한 글 확인하기 </title>

    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f6fff7;
        }

        .custom-card {
            max-width: 600px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(40, 167, 69, 0.2);
        }

        .alert-success {
            background-color: #d4edda;
            color: #155724;
            border-color: #c3e6cb;
        }

        .text-primary {
            color: #28a745 !important;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background-color: #28a745;
            border-color: #28a745;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: #218838;
            border-color: #1e7e34;
        }

        .card-text {
            color: #333;
        }
    </style>

</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <div class="custom-card mx-auto mt-5 text-center">
        <div class="alert alert-success fw-bold mb-4" role="alert">
            작성하신 글이 등록되었습니다!
        </div>
        <div class="card shadow-sm mb-4">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h4 class="card-title text-primary mb-3">{{title}}</h4>
                <hr>
                <p class="card-text fs-5" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">{{content}}</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <a href="/menus" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg shadow-sm mt-2">목록으로 돌아가기</a>
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>